<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4894224>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 35–50. Luticola evkae Kopalová sp. nov. Light (LM) and scanning electron micrographs (SEM). Type specimens from James Ross Island. Figs 35–47. LM of specimens from the type population. Fig. 48. SEM of external valve view. Fig. 49. SEM of detail of the raphe endings. Fig. 50. SEM of detail of the central raphe endings. LM scale bar = 10 µm. SEM scale bars = 2 µm." ;
